  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>For you, impending death is a call to wrath.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Str 13, Con 13, orc or half-orc, Diehard, Endurance, base attack bonus +6.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You are not staggered while using the Diehard feat, but if you take a move and a standard action or a full-round action while you are at 0 or fewer hit points you take 1 point of damage. Further, while using the Diehard feat, you gain a +2 bonus on melee attacks and damage rolls.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>When you are at 0 or fewer hit points, you can spend 2 stamina points to avoid taking damage when you take both a move and a standard action or a full-round action.",
